item.dc:creator: cb.en.u4mee21034
item.content:encoded:
At TeKovai, we believe that technology should work for you.

We as a company believe that technology should be made in such a way that it should adapt to the customer's needs and requirements and not the other way around. Our products are designed to be user-friendly, easy to use and fast, while satisfying our customer's complex business requirements. For us, perfection is of paramount importance. Hence, our products are designed from ground up using proven technology, while not compromising in key areas like performance and security.

lEARN MORE ABOUT US

Why do we do what we do?

The world is continuously changing at a very rapid pace. Business requirements are becoming more and more complex, and the demand for products that can keep up with these requirements is on the rise. Most products that are there in the market today are mass market products, designed to satisfy everyone. However, our products are built from the ground up using proven technology, keeping in mind the requirements of our customers. For example, our product, Extra POS, integrates with Extra ERP, which is built using technologies like React.js and SQL server, integrated with a seamless browser-based interface. This results in a rich, dynamic and easy to use front end, coupled with a robust, proven backend. Moreover, integrations with other third party systems like Oracle EBS and SAP allows for quick and effective implementations with existing systems.

Extra pos erp system

Tell us what your requirements are and we will try to make it happen.

Contact us today and tell us your business's requirements and we will be happy to assist. With an experienced team of developers led by two Chartered Accountants with 40+ years of industrial and technical experience, we are always ready to assist you to meet your unique business requirements. Please click on the button below to be redirected to the contact form.

item.title: Management
item.dc:creator: cb.en.u4mee21034
item.content:encoded:
Sudarshan Sarma is a cross functional professional with qualifications in finance and a passion for leveraging the power of technology to help business through improved processes and actionable reporting. He brings an excellent blend of deep domain knowledge in Finance and Supply Chain coupled with solid technical understanding gained over 20 years of experience in ERP Consulting, Software Development and IT Management.

Qualified as a Chartered Accountant (India) and a Certified Practising Accountant (Australia), he held multiple roles such as Chief Information Officer, Project Manager, Subject matter expert in Finance and Supply Chain modules, Finance executive etc. He has worked in many countries around the Asia Pacific region including India, New Zealand, Fiji, Saudi Arabia, Qatar, Singapore etc.

He is a Director at Tekovai Solutions India Pvt Limited and heads Product Development.

Rammohan Narayanan, is a Chartered Accountant and a Certified Information Systems Auditor. Ram has over 17 years of experience in ERP Consulting, Software Development and Systems Audit areas and has worked with different multi-national companies in United States, Europe, Australia and India.

During his vast career in ERP Consulting, he worked in various capacity including program manager, Account manager, project manager and Subject matter expert in Finance, projects and supply chain modules.

item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: cb.en.u4mee21034
item.content:encoded:
Who are we?

TeKovai is a company that was started to make technology work for the customer and not the other way around. Headed by two Chartered Accountants with more than 40 years of combined experience in both industry and technology, the company aims to build products that will meet their complex and dynamic business requirements in all areas.

What do we do?

We are a company that builds products that meet our customer's complex and continuously changing requirements. From complex ERP systems designed for medium to large scale users, to systems designed to work with a single server, our aim is to provide our customers with products that are fast, fluid, reliable and secure. Our suite of products includes ExtraPOS, an Integrated POS and ERP system with a browser based interface.

Check out extra pos

Perfection. The heart of everything we do.

We firmly believe that there is no point in a product if it is not perfect. Every button, every frame and every element in our products have been selected or designed to ensure that the product is seamless, fluid and fast. From aesthetic colours that are soft on the eye for the main screens, to vibrant colours to warn or indicate changes, everything has been selected keeping its purpose in mind. Moreover, our products use the latest and most reliable technology, ensuring that your application remains up to date.

Technologies that we have experience with:

Mass market products may check 9 out of 10 boxes. However, we are here to check all 10 boxes for you.

Voice of our Customers

Our vision is to bring a world-class shopping experience to Fiji. To achieve this, we needed a software that could support our entire business process with seamless integration between the customer facing point-of-sale and the backend ERP to manage our supply chain, inventory and finance. We also needed a range of actionable reports to help with decision making. Tekovai Solutions worked closely with us to deliver and implement a software that ticks all the boxes. We are impressed by the business knowledge and technical skills of the team and are very happy with the software.

- Kavishay Abhimannu, Managing Director, Extra Super Market, Fiji
